text: Akhunovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Akhunovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 2,449 as of 2010. There are 55 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Akhunovo, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
